title: my tears ricochet
description:
It's a track 5 so you know what that means... all of the emotions! What is Taylor truly referring to in "my tears ricochet"? We are pointing our fingers at you, he who shall not be named!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? There's lots of ways to contact us!
